<h2 id="settle-all-invoices-on-july-1" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-receivable/customer-payment-settle-multiple-invoices-multiple-discount-periods.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">Settle all invoices on July 1</h2>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-receivable/customer-payment-settle-multiple-invoices-multiple-discount-periods.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">If Arnie creates a payment journal to fully settle these invoices on July 1, the payment is 2,980.00. Arnie creates a payment for customer 4032 and then opens the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-receivable/customer-payment-settle-multiple-invoices-multiple-discount-periods.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">Settle transactions</strong> page. On the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-receivable/customer-payment-settle-multiple-invoices-multiple-discount-periods.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">Settle transactions</strong> page, Arnie marks all three invoice lines for settlement:</p>
