<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/accounts-receivable/customer-payment-settle-multiple-invoices-multiple-discount-periods.md" sourcestartlinenumber="65">The payment for invoice FTI-10042 is 990.00. A cash discount of 1 percent, or 10.00 is taken. Although July 1 is after the period that qualifies for the 2-percent discount, it's still in the period that qualifies for the 1-percent discount.</li>
</ul>
